{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/49300/extras/COTA_Brand_Gif.gif?t=1734532661\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Commander: Conquest of the Americas challenges you to rewrite history by leading a European nation to conquer and colonize the New World. From the Caribbean to Hudson Bay, build settlements and manage them strategically by optimizing resources, production, and trade routes. Balance relationships with rival nations and Native American tribes\u2014forge alliances or risk open conflict to secure your foothold.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/49300/extras/Trade.gif?t=1734532661\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Naval dominance is crucial: command up to 30 ships in intense real-time tactical battles, deciding between a fleet-wide RTS perspective or direct control of individual vessels. Adapt your strategies to the dynamic world around you, where diplomacy, exploration, and military power all play key roles in achieving success.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/49300/extras/Balance.gif?t=1734532661\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Features:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Shape the New World:</strong> Choose from seven European nations, each with unique strengths and challenges.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Dynamic Colony Management:</strong> Build and sustain settlements by managing resources, military strength, and trade.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Expansive Territories:</strong> Explore the vast Americas, from tropical Caribbean islands to the icy waters of Hudson Bay.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Tactical Naval Combat:</strong> Lead fleets in real-time battles with up to 30 ships, offering multiple control modes.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Diplomatic Depth:</strong> Navigate complex relationships with both European powers and Native tribes to secure your dominance.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Whether you\u2019re a shrewd trader, a cunning diplomat, or a fearless naval commander, the New World awaits your vision and ambition.</strong><br>\t\t\t\t\t\t</p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Founding Father","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/49300/b9000050028a786cac11f4e95c7f1bfc6fd3d886.jpg"},{"name":"Peace maker","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/49300/3fa19ad66fefd00c2aa6f21318ac2f60a0a0f96d.jpg"},{"name":"Naval Rookie","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/49300/e0b8fbc3a240a8014e13fcad85cb519b788fc3fb.jpg"},{"name":"Trading Rookie","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/49300/6be0731bd96397f81843c41be450b0a803b791e9.jpg"},{"name":"Survivor","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/49300/feaa5f56b52c888d43a17ff98920d3e359d0e9ed.jpg"},{"name":"Diplomat","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/49300/e525d430f79101e8aff53fa9c72e6e69a407f623.jpg"},{"name":"The Armada","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/49300/58ac926b94609b0765ae3af79ba9842c578322a8.jpg"},{"name":"Master and Commander","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/49300/6fe70f1f8e4bf48afe5535b68c7c8f3721fab4b7.jpg"},{"name":"Leader","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/49300/588556d30a42f6c81a047c2014c451e05d9bdce2.jpg"},{"name":"Boarder","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/49300/b6210f20be023202d56985c115345783268b842b.jpg"}],"total":50},"backgroun